### ✔ What `$loop->iteration` does

Inside a `@foreach` loop, Laravel automatically creates a **loop variable**.
`$loop->iteration` gives the **current row number starting from 1**.

Example:

@foreach($categories as $category)

<tr>
    <td>{{ $loop->iteration }}</td>
    <td>{{ $category->name }}</td>
</tr>
@endforeach




